# 6. Installing and Managing Services

```yaml
---
- name: Install and start Apache
  hosts: localhost
  become: yes

  tasks:
    - name: Install Apache
      apt:
        name: apache2
        state: present

    - name: Start apache2
      service:
        name: apache2
        state: started
```

Check:

systemctl status apache2

