# 10. Firewall + Services

```yaml
- name: Setup Apache and firewall
  hosts: all
  become: yes

  tasks:
    - name: Install Apache
      yum:
        name: httpd
        state: present

    - name: Start Apache
      service:
        name: httpd
        state: started

    - name: Allow HTTP
      firewalld:
        service: http
        permanent: true
        state: enabled

    - name: Reload firewalld
      service:
        name: firewalld
        state: reloaded
```

Check:

```bash
firewall-cmd --list-all
```

