# 16. Kill Processes (Troubleshooting)

```yaml
- name: Kill process
  hosts: all

  tasks:
    - name: Find process
      shell: "pgrep -f top"
      register: running_process

    - name: Kill process
      command: kill {{ item }}
      loop: "{{ running_process.stdout_lines }}"
      ignore_errors: yes
```

